its%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreece-six-day-workweek-productivity-plan-may-not-work-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix-day%20workweek%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20backlash%2C%20according%20to%20CNBC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20policy%20allows%20extra%20hours%20in%20specific%20industries%20as%C2%A0%26quot%3Ban%20exceptional%20measure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEmployees%20will%20receive%2040%25%20more%20pay%20for%20extra%20hours%20worked%20under%20the%20new%20regulation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Greek%20government%20responded%20to%20backlash%20about%20its%20new%20six-day%20workweek%20policy%20and%20said%20the%20regulation%20doesn't%20change%20the%20current%20workweek%2C%20according%20to%20a%20CNBC%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F07%2F09%2Fgreece-defends-six-day-work-week-says-it-is-an-exceptional-measure.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20this%20new%20regulation%20does%20not%20in%20any%20way%20affect%20the%20established%205-day%2F40-hour%20working%20week%20mandated%20by%20Greek%20law%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20establish%20a%20new%206-day%20working%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Greek%20Minister%20of%20Labour%20and%20Social%20Security%20Niki%20Kerameus%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Kerameus%20said%20it%20provides%20the%20option%20of%20working%20an%20additional%20day%20%26quot%3Bin%20limited%20circumstances%26quot%3B%20and%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20exceptional%20measure%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20regulation%20gives%20employees%20in%20some%20industries%20the%20option%20to%20work%2048%20hours%20a%20week.%20Employees%20can%20do%20so%20by%20working%20an%20extra%20two%20hours%20daily%20or%20adding%20an%20eight-hour%20shift%20to%20their%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKerameus%20said%20the%20businesses%20impacted%20are%20only%20those%20that%20operate%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20five%20to%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20with%20rotating%20shifts.%20The%20policy%20will%20apply%20to%20industries%20like%20agriculture%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20some%20service%20industries.%20Food%20and%20travel%20businesses%20are%20excluded%20from%20the%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Greek%20government%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fjul%2F01%2Fgreece-introduces-growth-oriented-six-day-working-week%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehas%20said%20a%2048-hour%20workweek%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20boost%20productivity%20as%20the%20country%20struggles%20with%20a%20worker%20shortage%20and%20an%20overall%20population%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20policy%20has%20been%20controversial%20since%20it%20was%20approved%20in%20September%2C%20especially%20as%20other%20countries%20experiment%20by%20going%20the%20other%20way%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-could-be-here-sooner-than-you-think-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efour-day%20workweek%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20it%20was%20proposed%2C%20thousands%20of%20workers%20went%20on%20strike%20to%20protest%20the%20package%20of%20new%20labor%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20policy%20is%20voluntary%2C%20labor%20unions%20and%20other%20critics%20have%20expressed%20concern%20about%20it%20expanding%20to%20other%20industries.%20There%20are%20also%20concerns%20about%20it%20leading%20to%20employees%20being%20overworked%20and%20compensated%20unfairly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Kerameus%20said%20the%20extra%20working%20day%20is%20only%20applicable%20in%20situations%20of%20increased%20workload%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20She%20also%20said%20the%20new%20policy%20would%20allow%20employees%20to%20declare%20extra%20time%20legally%20so%20that%20they%20can%20be%20compensated%20fairly.%20Employees%20who%20work%20the%20extra%20hours%20will%20see%20a%2040%25%20jump%20in%20pay%20for%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKerameus%20said%20the%20law%20also%20provides%20more%20protection%20for%20workers%2C%20like%20guaranteed%20days%20off%2C%20set%20working%20hours%2C%20and%20measures%20to%20prevent%20wrongful%20termination%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20six-day%20workweeks%20are%20uncommon%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20has%20similar%20guidelines.%20According%20to%20its%20website%2C%20employees%20shouldn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuropa.eu%2Fyoureurope%2Fbusiness%2Fhuman-resources%2Fworking-hours-holiday-leave%2Fworking-hours%2Findex_en.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%2048%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20average.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20there%20are%20no%20federal%20limits%20on%20the%20total%20hours%20an%20employee%20can%20work%20so%20long%20as%20they%20receive%20overtime%20pay%20after%20working%20more%20than%2040%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Greek%20government%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreece-government-defending-new-6-day-workweek-policy-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720547049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d53ca268f62ba18a8695b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreece-government-defending-new-6-day-workweek-policy-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Greek%20government%20said%20the%20new%20policy%20provides%20the%20option%20of%20working%20extra%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20exceptional%20measure%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20doesn't%20establish%20a%206-day%20working%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside