2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc134kgdpd6do%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc134kgdpd6do.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc134kgdpd6do.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Mumbai%20Police%20Caught%20Politician's%20Son%2072%20Hours%20After%20BMW%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20mobile%20phone%20of%20a%20friend%20of%20the%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20BMW%20hit-and-run%20case%20led%20the%20police%20to%20Mihir%20Shah%2C%20who%20had%20fled%20the%20scene%20after%20allegedly%20running%20over%20a%20woman%20with%20his%20luxury%20car%20on%20Sunday.%20It%20took%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20three%20days%20to%20catch%20the%20accused%20because%20he%2C%20along%20with%20his%20mother%20and%20sisters%2C%20had%20switched%20off%20their%20mobile%20phones%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20been%20searching%20for%20the%20family%20members%20using%20their%20car%20number.%20The%20phone%20number%20of%20Mihir's%20friend%20was%20also%20under%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BMW%20car%20hit%20fish-seller%20couple%20Pradeep%20Nakhwa%20and%20Kaveri%20Nakhwa%20in%20Worli%20early%20on%20Sunday.%20The%2024-year-old%20was%20allegedly%20behind%20the%20wheels%20at%20the%20time%20while%20his%20driver%2C%20Rajrishi%20Bidawat%2C%20was%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat.%20The%20woman%20was%20dragged%20for%20nearly%201.5%20kilometres.%20Afterward%2C%20Shah%20and%20Bidawat%20exchanged%20seats%20and%20mowed%20her%20down%20again%20while%20reversing%20the%20car%2C%20police%20said.%20They%20then%20sped%20away%20and%20Shah%20was%20missing%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20he%20left%20the%20BMW%20near%20Kala%20Nagar%20in%20Bandra%20and%20went%20to%20his%20girlfriend's%20house%20in%20Goregaon.%20The%20girlfriend%20informed%20his%20sister%20about%20the%20accident%20after%20she%20came%20to%20her%20house%2C%20picked%20him%20up%20and%20drove%20to%20their%20house%20in%20Borivali.%20From%20there%2C%20the%20family%20-%20his%20mother%20(Meena)%20and%20two%20sisters%20(Puja%20and%20Kinjal)%20-%20and%20the%20friend%20(Avdeep)%20left%20for%20a%20resort%20in%20Shahpur%2C%20nearly%2070%20km%20from%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Was%20Mihir%20Shah%20Caught%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20night%2C%20Mihir%20Shah%20separated%20from%20his%20family%20and%20came%20with%20his%20friend%20to%20Virar%2C%20around%2065%20km%20from%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20the%20friend%20switched%20on%20his%20phone%20for%2015%20minutes%20and%20the%20police%20got%20his%20location%20and%20then%20arrested%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2012%20people%2C%20including%20Shah's%20mother%20and%20sisters%2C%20were%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah%20is%20the%20son%20of%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20party%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Palghar%20district%2C%20Rajesh%20Shah.%20He%20allegedly%20called%20his%20father%20after%20the%20crash%20who%20then%20asked%20him%20to%20escape.%20Rajesh%20Shah%20soon%20reached%20the%20spot%C2%A0%20and%20was%20planning%20to%20tow%20the%20BMW%20but%20a%20patrolling%20team%2C%20alerted%20by%20Kaveri%20Nakhwa's%20husband%2C%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20caught%20him%20and%20the%20driver%2C%20Bidawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Shah%20and%20Bidawat%20were%20produced%20in%20the%20court%20of%20Chief%20Metropolitan%20Magistrate%20(Sewree)%20SP%20Bhosale%20yesterday%20and%20were%20remanded%20in%2014-day%20judicial%20and%20one-day%20police%20custody%2C%20respectively.%20Shah%20was%20charged%20for%20allegedly%20providing%20misinformation%20and%20destruction%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Shah%20was%2C%20however%2C%20granted%20bail%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720542780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.