%20Mhambrey%20and%20fielding%20coach%20T.%20DIlip%20for%20their%20services%20and%20wished%20them%20luck%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Cricket%20Advisory%20Committee%20comprising%20Mr%20Ashok%20Malhotra%2C%20Mr%20Jatin%20Paranjpe%20and%20Ms%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sulakshana%20Naik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F61804-sulakshana-madhukar-naik-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESulakshana%20Naik%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20unanimously%20recommended%20Mr%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20as%20the%20Head%20Coach%20of%20Team%20India%20(Senior%20Men).%20The%20former%20India%20batter%20will%20take%20charge%20from%20the%20upcoming%20away%20series%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20where%20Team%20India%20are%20set%20to%20play%203%20ODIs%20%26amp%3B%203%20T20Is%20starting%20July%2027%2C%202024.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20had%20invited%20applications%20for%20the%20said%20position%20on%20May%2013th%20to%20appoint%20Mr%20Rahul%20Dravid's%20successor%2C%20whose%20term%20got%20over%20after%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20would%20like%20to%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20express%20its%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20Mr%20Dravid%20for%20his%20outstanding%20service%20as%20Head%20Coach.%20Dravid's%20tenure%20was%20marked%20by%20significant%20achievements%3B%20the%20most%20noteworthy%20being%20crowned%20champions%20of%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%202024.%20Team%20India%20also%20finished%20as%20runners-up%20in%20the%20ICC%2050-over%20World%20Cup%2C%202023%20hosted%20in%20India%20%26amp%3B%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20in%202023%20hosted%20in%20England.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20the%20team's%20dominance%20in%20bilateral%20series%20at%20home%2C%20Dravid's%20dedication%20to%20nurturing%20young%20talent%20and%20instilling%20discipline%20and%20sportsmanship%20in%20the%20team%20has%20been%20exemplary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20also%20congratulates%20Mr%20Paras%20Mhambrey%20(Bowling%20Coach)%2C%20Mr%20T.%20Dilip%20(Fielding%20Coach)%20and%20Mr%20Vikram%20Rathour%20(Batting%20Coach)%20on%20a%20highly%20successful%20tenure.%20The%20BCCI%20values%20their%20contribution%20and%20wishes%20them%20the%20best%20going%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20welcomes%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20in%20his%20role%20with%20Team%20India.%20The%20former%20Indian%20opener%20brings%20with%20him%20a%20wealth%20of%20experience%20and%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20game.%20Known%20for%20his%20exceptional%20batting%20prowess%20and%20strategic%20acumen%2C%20Gambhir%20has%20been%20a%20pivotal%20figure%20in%20Indian%20cricket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20remarkable%20contributions%20to%20the%20Indian%20team%20that%20include%20crucial%20performances%20in%20the%202007%20ICC%20World%20T20%20and%20the%202011%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20have%20cemented%20his%20legacy%20as%20one%20of%20the%20sport's%20greats.%20Gambhir%20also%20led%20his%20IPL%20franchise%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20to%20two%20title%20victories%20in%202012%20and%202014.%20In%20his%20role%20as%20mentor%20with%20KKR%20in%202024%2C%20Gambhir%20helped%20the%20team%20secure%20its%20third%20IPL%20title.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20his%20new%20role%20as%20Head%20Coach%20of%20Team%20India%2C%20Gambhir%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20overseeing%20the%20development%20and%20performance%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20His%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20developing%20a%20culture%20of%20excellence%2C%20discipline%2C%20and%20teamwork%2C%20while%20also%20nurturing%20young%20talent%20and%20preparing%20the%20team%20for%20future%20challenges%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20press%20release%20from%20BCCI%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720538880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim