blished%22%3A1720536234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111612336%2Cimgsize-18774.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fgladiator-2-official-trailer-out-paul-mescals-fierce-face-off-against-pedro-pascal-and-denzel-washington-in-ridley-scotts-action-flick-watch%2Farticleshow%2F111612349.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111612349.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E'Gladiator%202'%20trailer%20features%20Paul%20Mescal%20as%20Lucius%2C%20with%20Pedro%20Pascal%2C%20Denzel%20Washington%2C%20Joseph%20Quinn%2C%20and%20Fred%20Hechinger%20in%20key%20roles.%20Directed%20by%20Ridley%20Scott%2C%20the%20film%20releases%20November%2022.%20Connie%20Nielsen%20returns.%20Hans%20Zimmer%20composes%20the%20score.%20In%20a%20Vanity%20Fair%20interview%2C%20Scott%20praised%20Mescal%E2%80%99s%20performance.%20Lucius%20returns%20to%20Rome%20as%20a%20gladiator.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fgladiator-2-official-trailer-out-paul-mescals-fierce-face-off-against-pedro-pascal-and-denzel-washington-in-ridley-scotts-action-flick-watch%2Farticleshow%2F111612349.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Extends%20Ban%20On%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun's%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20on%20pro-Khalistan%20group%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20(SFJ)%2C%20founded%20by%20US-based%20lawyer%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20has%20been%20extended%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20five%20years%20for%20its%20relentless%20anti-India%20activities.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20a%20notification%20issued%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20said%20SFJ%20was%20declared%20a%20banned%20organisation%20five%20years%20ago%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20for%20its%20anti-national%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20said%20the%20Central%20government%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20SFJ%20continues%20to%20indulge%20in%20activities%20which%20are%20prejudicial%20to%20the%20integrity%20and%20security%20of%20the%20country%20and%20is%20involved%20in%20anti-national%20and%20subversive%20activities%20in%20Punjab%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20intended%20to%20disrupt%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20SFJ%20is%20in%20close%20touch%20with%20militant%20outfits%20and%20activists%2C%20and%20is%20supporting%20a%20violent%20form%20of%20extremism%20and%20militancy%20in%20Punjab%20and%20elsewhere%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20sovereign%20Khalistan%20out%20of%20territory%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pro-Khalistan%20separatist%20group%20is%20encouraging%20and%20aiding%20the%20activities%20for%20the%20secession%20of%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20territory%20and%20supporting%20separatist%20groups%20fighting%20for%20this%20purpose%20in%20India%20and%20elsewhere%20by%20indulging%20in%20activities%20and%20articulations%20intended%20to%20disrupt%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Ministry%20said%20the%20government%20feels%20that%20if%20the%20unlawful%20activities%20of%20SFJ%20are%20not%20curbed%20and%20controlled%20immediately%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20escalate%20its%20subversive%20activities%20including%20attempts%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20Khalistan%20nation%20out%20of%20the%20territory%20of%20India%20by%20destabilising%20the%20government%20established%20by%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SFJ%20continues%20to%20advocate%20the%20secession%20of%20Punjab%20from%20India%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20Khalistan%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20propagate%20anti-national%20and%20separatist%20sentiments%20prejudicial%20to%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20security%20of%20the%20country%20and%20escalates%20secessionist%20movements%2C%20and%20support%20militancy%20and%20incite%20violence%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20therefore%2C%20in%20exercise%20of%20the%20powers%20conferred%20by%20sub-sections%20(1)%20and%20(3)%20of%20section%203%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%20(37%20of%201967)%2C%20the%20central%20government%20hereby%20extends%20the%20declaration%20of%20the%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20as%20an%20unlawful%20association%20and%20directs%20that%20this%20notification%20shall%2C%20subject%20to%20any%20order%20that%20may%20be%20made%20under%20section%204%20of%20the%20said%20Act%2C%20have%20effect%20for%20a%20further%20period%20of%20five%20years%20from%2010th%20day%20of%20July%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESFJ%20was%20founded%20by%20US-based%20Pannun%2C%20who%20was%20also%20declared%20as%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20government.%20It%20had%20also%20carried%20out%20a%20campaign%20for%20a%20referendum%20for%20a%20separate%20Khalistan%20about%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPannun%2C%20who%20holds%20dual%20citizenship%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%2C%20is%20wanted%20in%20India%20on%20terror%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20was%20extradited%20to%20the%20US%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20an%20%26quot%3Bindependent%20and%20sovereign%20country%26quot%3B%20in%20Punjab.%20It%20openly%20espouses%20the%20cause%20of%20Khalistan%20and%20in%20that%20process%20challenges%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESFJ%20was%20first%20declared%20a%20banned%20organisation%20under%20the%20UAPA%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720536060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd10hkbbo_pannun3_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-extends-ban-on-gurpatwant-singh-pannuns-sikhs-for-justice-by-5-years-6068470%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20extended%20the%20ban%20imposed%20on%20pro-Khalistan%20group%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20(SFJ)%20for%20five%20years%20for%20its%20anti-India%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-extends-ban-on-gurpatwant-singh-pannuns-sikhs-for-justice-by-5-years-6068470%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-extends-ban-on-gurpatwant-singh-pannuns-sikhs-for-justice-by-5-years-6068470%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-extends-ban-on-gurpatwant-singh-pannuns-sikhs-for-justice-by-5-years-6068470%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bank%20transfers%20made%20by%20Tate%20brothers%20were%20'entirely%20orthodox'%2C%20lawyer%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720535640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-andrew-tate-tristan_6547091.jpg%3F20240508171518%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbank-transfers-made-by-tate-brothers-were-entirely-orthodox-lawyer-says-13175630%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bank%20transfers%20made%20by%20controversial%20social%20media%20influencer%20Andrew%20Tate%20and%20his%20brother%20Tristan%20were%20%26quot%3Bentirely%20orthodox%26quot%3B%2C%20their%20lawyer%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbank-transfers-made-by-tate-brothers-were-entirely-orthod