habahar%20Konarak%20airport%20in%20southern%20Iran%20when%C2%A0local%20technician%20Abolfazl%20Amiri%20was%20pulled%20into%20the%20engine%20of%20a%20Boeing%20passenger%20jet%20while%20performing%20routine%20maintenance%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bild.de%2Fnews%2Fausland%2Fnach-der-landung-mechaniker-von-triebwerk-angesaugt-tot-668cce13bdb18e1605d7d2cb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBild%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20Boeing%20arrived%20in%20Tehran%20early%20at%207%3A15%20am%20and%20landed%20safely%20in%20Chabahar%20Konarak%20airport.%20As%20per%20standard%20practice%2C%20the%20engine%20on%20the%20right-hand%20side%20was%20turned%20on%20for%20a%20test%20check%20with%20the%20cover%20flaps%20open.%20A%20safety%20area%20had%20also%20been%20set%20up%20around%20the%20engine%20as%20required.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20Mr%20Amiri%20realised%20he%20had%20forgotten%20a%20tool%20on%20the%20engine%2C%20he%20went%20back%20towards%20the%20plane%20to%20retrieve%20it.%C2%A0As%20he%20went%20close%20to%20the%20turbine%2C%20he%20was%20sucked%20in%20and%20killed%20before%20the%20engine%20caught%20fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20airport%20fire%20brigade%20arrived%20quickly%20and%20extinguished%20the%20fire%20with%20water%2C%20rescuers%20were%20only%20able%20to%20recover%20the%20remains%20of%20the%20mechanic.%20The%20plane%20operated%20by%20domestic%20carrier%20Varesh%20Airlines%20was%20grounded%20for%20repairs%2C%20and%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20accident%20was%20ordered%20by%20Iran's%20aviation%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20similar%20incident%20happened%20when%20a%20man%20lost%20his%20life%20after%20being%20pulled%20into%20the%20engine%20of%20a%20KLM%20passenger%20plane%20at%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0dd9pxnd0lo%5C%22%3E%20Amsterdam's%20Schiphol%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Passengers%20and%20crew%20members%20reportedly%20witnessed%20the%20tragic%20death%20before%20emergency%20services%20rushed%20to%20the%20scene.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20Dutch%20newspaper%20De%20Telegraaf%2C%20witnesses%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bhellish%20noise%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20person%20was%20sucked%20into%20the%20jet%20turbine.%C2%A0It%20is%20understood%20the%20man%20died%20after%20deliberately%20climbing%20into%20the%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20airport%20employee%20died%20after%20being%20sucked%20into%20a%20Delta%20passenger%20plane%20engine%20in%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720532040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fmikekg18_boeing-passenger-jet_625x300_09_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fplane-mechanic-in-iran-dies-after-getting-sucked-into-boeing-jets-engine-6068640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20happened%20when%20local%20technician%20Abolfazl%20Amiri%20was%20pulled%20into%20the%20engine%20of%20a%20Boeing%20passenger%20jet%20while%20performing%20routine%20maintenance%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fplane-mechanic-in-iran-dies-after-getting-sucked-into-boeing-jets-engine-6068640%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fplane-mechanic-in-iran-dies-after-getting-sucked-into-boeing-jets-engine-6068640%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fplane-mechanic-in-iran-dies-after-getting-sucked-into-boeing-jets-engine-6068640%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Proptechs%20experience%20traffic%20surge%20as%20AI%20enhances%20consumer%20experience%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720532019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F26%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1716741083-6802.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fproptechs-experience-traffic-surge-as-ai-enhances-consumer-experience-124070900877_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20indicate%20that%20the%20Indian%20proptech%20market%20is%20projected%20to%20grow%209.6%20per%20cent%20annually%20from%202021%20to%202025%2C%20reaching%20a%20%24100%20billion%20valuation%20by%202030%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fproptechs-experience-traffic-surge-as-ai-enhances-consumer-experience-124070900877_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fproptechs-experience-traffic-surge-as-ai-enhances-consumer-experience-124070900877_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fproptechs-experience-traffic-surge-as-ai-enhances-consumer-experience-124070900877_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThey%20Take%20Votes%2C%20Treat%20Us%20Like%20Garbage%26quot%3B%3A%20Husband%20Of%20BMW%20Hit-And-Run%20Victim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah%2C%20who%20allegedly%20rammed%20a%20couple%20with%20his%20BMW%20on%20Sunday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmain-accused-in-mumbai-bmw-hit-and-run-case-mihir-shah-arrested-6067307%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20for%20the%20man%20who%20saw%20his%20wife%20being%20dragged%20under%20the%20wheels%20of%20the%20car%20in%20front%20of%20him%20and%20the%20daughter%20who%20saw%20her%20mother%20suffer%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20action%20means%20little%20to%20none.%20%26quot%3BHe%20dragged%20her%20(under%20the%20wheels)%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20There's%20no%20one%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pradeep%20Nakhwa%20breaking%20down%20into%20tears%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20poor.%20Who%20is%20there%20to%20support%20us%20or%20get%20us%20justice%3F%20Today%2C%20he%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20jail.%20Tomorrow%20he%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20and%20then%20he%20will%20get%20bail.%20He%20will%20be%20released%20and%20then%20this%20case%20will%20be%20dragged%20on.%20Where%20will%20we%20get%20the%20money%20(to%20fight%20the%20case)%3F%20How%20will%20we%20hire%20a%20lawyer%3F%20Who%20is%20there%20for%20us%3F%20Politicians%20don't%20care%20for%20us.%20He%20(the%20accused)%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20leader.%20He%20has%20money.%20We%20have%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Nakhwa%20who%20also%20got%20injured%20in%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shah%20is%20the%20son%20of%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20party%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Palghar%20district%2C%20Rajesh%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Mihir%20Shah)was%20arrested%20three%20days%20after%20the%20accident.%20Why%20was%20he%20hiding%3F%20If%20he%20didn't%20do%20anything%2C%20if%20he%20didn't%20have%20alcohol%20or%20drugs%2C%20why%20did%20he%20run%3F%20He%20abandoned%20the%20vehicle%20after%20the%20crash%2C%20broke%20the%20number%20plate%20and%20went%20into%20hiding%2C%20why%3F%20He%20won't%20have%20any%20trace%20of%20alcohol%20in%20his%20blood%20after%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Nakhwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fish-seller%20couple%20Pradeep%20Nakhwa%20and%20Kaveri%20Nakhwa%20was%20headed%20home%20after%20buying%20fish%20from%20Sassoon%20Dock%20early%20on%20Sunday%20when%20they%20were%20hit%20by%20the%20luxury%20car%20from%20behind.%20The%2024-year-old%20was%20allegedly%20behind%20the%20wheels%20at%20the%20time%20while%20his%20driver%2C%20Rajrishi%20Bidawat%2C%20was%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaging%20with%20sorrow%2C%20Mr%20Nakhwa%20wondered%20why%20none%20of%20the%20politicians%20inquired%20after%20them%3A%20%26quot%3BHas%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20visited%20us%3F%20Has%20Eknath%20Shinde%20come%20to%20our%20home%20to%20know%20what%20happened%3F%20Is%20Ajit%20Pawar%20here%3F%20They%20only%20care%20for%20the%20chair.%20Power%20has%20blinded%20all%20of%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20only%20remember%20us%20for%20votes.%20They%20forget%20us%20after%20that.%20Public%20is%20garbage%20for%20them.%20They%20talk%20about%20ladli%20behna%20yojna.%20Your%20'ladli%20behna'%20has%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Nakhwa%2C%20choking%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20head%20Eknath%20Shinde%20asserted%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%2C%20whether%20rich%2C%20influential%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20spared%20if%20found%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%2C%20whether%20rich%2C%20influential%20or%20the%20offspring%20of%20bureaucrats%20or%20ministers%2C%20affiliated%20with%20any%20party%2C%20will%20have%20immunity%20as%20long%20as%20I%20am%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20produced%20by%20police%20in%20court%20yesterday%20showed%20Nakhwa%20being%20dragged%20by%20the%20car%20for%201.5%20kilometres.%20It%20showed%20Mihir%20Shah%20and%20Bidawat%20pulling%20the%20woman%20off%20the%20engine%20bay%20and%20placing%20her%20on%20the%20road.%20They%20then%20exchanged%20seats%20and%20mowed%20her%20down%20again%20while%20reversing%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20would%20have%20been%20alive%20today%20if%20he%20hadn't%20run%20his%20car%20over%20her%20again%20while%20reversing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20her%20grieving%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daughter%2C%20sitting%20next%20to%20her%20father%2C%20said%20she%20wants%20the%20accused%20to%20be%20hanged%2C%20gesturing%20with%20her%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20pain.%20She%20was%20badly%20injured.%20I%20saw%20her%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20she%20was%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20pain.%20I%20want%20justice%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20crying%20inconsolably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20allegedly%20sped%20away%20after%20running%20over%20the%20woman.%20But%20the%20vehicle's%20engine%20stalled%20after%20some%20time.%20Mihir%20then%20allegedly%20called%20his%20father%20Rajesh%20Shah%20from%20his%20driver's%20phone%20and%20told%20him%20about%20the%20accident%20who%20in%20turn%20asked%20him%20to%20escape.%20Later%20Rajesh%20Shah%20planned%20to%20tow%20the%20BMW%20from%20there%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20Kaveri%20Nakhwa's%20husband%20Pradip%20and%20a%20witness%20had%20alerted%20the%20police%2C%20a%20patrolling%20team%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20caught%20Rajesh%20and%20Bidawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Shah%20and%20Bidawat%20were%20produced%20in%20the%20court%20of%20Chief%20Metropolitan%20Magistrate%20(Sewree)%20SP%20Bhosale%20yesterday%20and%20were%20remanded%20in%2014-day%20judicial%20and%20one-day%20police%20custody%2C%20respectively.%20Shah%20was%20charged%20for%20allegedly%20providing%20misinformation%20and%20destruction%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Shah%20was%2C%20however%2C%20later%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720531500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fe5hspb28_nakhwas_625x300_09_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-bmw-crash-why-did-he-run-family-of-bmw-hit-and-run-victim-wants-accused-hanged-6068550%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mihir%20Shah%2C%20who%20allegedly%20rammed%20a%20couple%20with%20his%20BMW%20on%20Sunday%2C%20was%20arrested%20%2C%20but%20for%20the%20man%20who%20saw%20his%20wife%20being%20dragged%20under%20the%20wheels%20of%20the%20car%20and%20the%20daughter%20who%20saw%20her%20mother%20suffer%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20action%20means%20little%20to%2