449%2Fharitha-kk-kerala-first-woman-captain-fishing-vessel-india-inspiring%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoining%20the%20Indian%20Navy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20could%20remember.%20However%2C%20when%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20through%2C%20she%20began%20searching%20for%20the%20next%20best%20alternative.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20be%20on%20a%20ship%20and%20was%20ready%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20took.%20A%209-5%20job%20is%20not%20for%20me.%20I%20wanted%20a%20job%20that%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20travel%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Romeeta%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fis1utsJJKMs%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fis1utsJJKMs%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20electrical%20engineering%2C%20she%20applied%20to%20the%20Shipping%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(SCI)%20for%20the%20position%20of%20an%20ETO.%20She%20shares%20that%20despite%20getting%20through%2C%20their%20batch%20was%20debarred.%20She%20then%20turned%20to%20the%20one%20with%20all%20the%20answers%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Goog